description: For the War Chest Update tonight, we're giving you a never-before-scene solo that Julian did for us. This guy is so damn hot. He's got a thick, long dick and a body that just won't quit.He only did two solos for us on video. One has already been released on DVD (in Rock Hard Regiment 3), but the one we are screening tonight has never been released. In the War Chest Update, Julian gets animated and works himself up to a big finish, in a way that only Julian can. Dang, I wish we had more of him! Sometimes, the hottest ones get away ...
title: Julian, Scene #01
